Groovy util classes that are "shared" between the CLI and user applications.

程序包org.springframework.boot.groovy的说明

Groovy util classes that are "shared" between the CLI and user applications. Classes is this package can be loaded from compiled user code. Not under the cli package in case we want to extract into a separate jar at a future date.
